name: Original Gangsters
description: $OG is a tribute to the pioneers of Solana—the original believers who helped shape the ecosystem into what it is today. More than just a meme,The $OG represents the history, the community, and the innovation, ensuring that Solana’s legacy remains alive while paving the way for the future. It is a cultural movement that embodies the resilience, vision, and spirit of the blockchain’s earliest adopters.
